Working with Widgets

Widgets are configured trough Widget Configuration Dialog. The dialog allows you to perform a search and to find the items that you want to present trough the widget, to select the data about this items and also to configure how the widget to be presented in the page - to select colors, to select if a grid to be displayed if table, to select if a header to be present and the type of the header etc.
